proximal humerus fracture.  Initially seen at ___, 
she was diagnosed with a proximal humerus fracture, was  
subsequently referred to your attention.  Seen and evaluated in 
the office, she demonstrated a displaced proximal humerus 
fracture and was referred to my attention out of concernfor 
